# Keep line endings sane cross-platform.
* text=auto
*.sh  text eol=lf
*.py  text eol=lf
*.ps1 text eol=crlf

# --- GitHub language bar (Linguist) ---
# The only .ps1 / .sh files in this repo are the per-OS install scripts (Windows / Unix). They are
# setup boilerplate, not the substance of the kit (a Markdown skill + Python tooling). Keep them out
# of the language statistics so the bar reflects the Python tooling, not whichever installer set is
# larger by bytes. (Markdown and images are already excluded by Linguist as prose / data.)
*.ps1 linguist-vendored
*.sh  linguist-vendored
